criterion_text: Evidence of emphysema on radiographic imaging.
Evidence of another form of liver disease.
History of poor adherence to treatment.
Evidence or history of toxic megacolon
Evidence of bleeding diathesis or coagulopathy
Evidence of a secondary form of hypertension.
Previous history of chronic chest pain.
Evidence of distant metastases of stage IV
History of sensitivity to radiation therapy
Significant degree of dysphagia, by history.
Clinical evidence of parenteral nutrition associated cholestasis
